    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Book your free ticket\n\nAdmission is free, but tickets are required.\n\nTickets will be available starting June 26 at 12:30 PM ET, online, by phone, or in person.\n\nThere is a limit of four tickets per account. Accounts exceeding this limit will have their tickets cancelled without notice.\n\nTickets will appear in patron accounts 48 hours before the concert.\n\nA Canada Day tradition in the heart of Ottawa!\n\nCelebrate July 1 with the National Arts Centre Orchestra in a special concert that brings together artists, music, and stories from across..."
      }
    ],
