    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "KILLABEATMAKER | The Feeling of Free |  Wed, Jul 8, 2026, 12:00 pm | Atrium O’Brien"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40965/killabeatmaker_pic_4__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "El español sigue al texto en inglés\n\nBrown bag lunches don’t have to be dull! Enjoy a free, music-filled midday break in the O'Brien Atrium. Bring your meal, grab a spot, and experience incredible live performances by talented artists. \n\nKillabeatmaker combines Colombian rhythms with Afrobeats, Amapiano and Cumbia. \n\nThe show brings a grooving and mystical combination through an energetic performance with unique instruments from their motherland. \n\nThe live band is made up of three musicians Guadalupe Giraldo on the drums, Colombian Gaita and main..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
